lead_paragraph: Dak Prescott's job was to win without Tony Romo when the Dallas Cowboys lost their 10-year starting quarterback to a preseason back injury after going 1-11 with him sidelined last season.

headline.print_headline: Prescott, Cowboys Headline Teams Winning Minus Injured Stars
